 Workflow Automation
Tools from thevibefounder's series on scaling business operations through AI.
General Workflow Automation
1. Zapier: Connects 6,000+ apps with AI-powered automation features.
2. Make: A visual drag-and-drop platform with built-in AI modules.
3. Pipedream: Developer-friendly automation with OpenAI and LangChain integrations.
4. n8n: Open-source, self-hosted alternative to Zapier.
Email & Marketing Automation
1. Sender AI: Automates personalized email and SMS campaigns.
2. Customer.io: Behavioral targeting using event-driven marketing automation.
3. Ortto: Combines customer data with GPT-powered content creation.
4. Brevo: AI-powered CRM automation for small to mid-sized businesses.
Sales & Lead Gen Automation
1. Apollo.io: AI-driven prospecting to automate outbound sequences at scale.
2. Clay.com: Data enrichment platform that creates hyper-personalized outreach.
3. Lavender AI: Real-time writing assistant for crafting high-performing cold emails.
4. Magical AI: Automates repetitive sales tasks to boost efficiency.
Analytics & Reporting Automation
1. Polymer Search: Instantly transforms spreadsheets into interactive AI dashboards.
2. DashThis: Automates marketing data visualization and insights.
3. MonkeyLearn: Uses AI for text analysis and automated dashboard creation.
4. SheetAI: Brings GPT-powered intelligence directly into Google Sheets.

3. Content Creation Automation
1. Jasper AI Workflows: Multi-step AI workflows for teams producing content at scale.
2. Copy.ai Workflows: Automates marketing campaigns using GPT-powered workflows.
3. Notion AI: Summarizes, rewrites, and organizes content inside Notion.
4. Outranking: AI-powered SEO platform for high-ranking blog content.
4. Chatbots & Support Automation
1. Tidio AI: Chatbots with intent detection for smarter customer conversations.
2. Intercom Fin AI: Resolves over 50% of support tickets automatically.
3. Drift: B2B AI platform with meeting scheduling and sales integrations.
4. Botpress: Open-source platform for building advanced AI chatbots.
